{
  "stem": "2522.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When I retired from Xerox, I started doing work in my specialty, leading to-- to-- to an assignment for General Motors to arbitrate a very major dispute of General Motors.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I always did public service, by the way, throughout my whole career.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I always was on government advisory commissions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In fact, I was offered a number of government posts from time to time, which I couldn't afford with a family of four.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I would not say that I went to the government because of some grand plan.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, I never would have thought that I would be offered a senior government post.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it just happened that I solved the problem for General Motors, and then the vice chairman of General Motors became Deputy Secretary of Defense and was-- was given the job to cut $72 billion dollars, largely through introduction of automation.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said, I have just the man who can do that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so I was offered a job down in Washington.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I'm just a good soldier, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I just-- you know, it's like in the partisans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, the guys ask me, well, go and walk in the front.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I'd walk in the front.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Atwood asked me walk in the front over really taking the Department of Defense apart.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, fine, I'll do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I did it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I'm very proud of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a wonderful, glorious association which I'm continuing with the Department of Defense.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is a-- somehow, I clicked very, very, very well with the military.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and they-- they consider me as one of the people who-- who they can trust.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
